            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Sora (OpenAI) leads on quality for text-to-video. Runway Gen-3 Alpha is strong for creative and commercial work. Pika and Kling offer solid free tiers. HeyGen and Synthesia focus on talking-head videos with AI avatars.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">How much does AI video generation cost?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button>
